Package: ssmbar
Title: Social Security Microsimulation Benefit Calculator
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R:
    person("Anthony", "Colavito", email = "colavito@crfb.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Anthony Colavito [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Anthony Colavito <colavito@crfb.org>
Description: Calculates Social Security retirement benefits for hypothetical
    workers using the exact formulas, rules, and parameters defined by the
    Social Security Administration. Supports preset worker types (very low, low,
    medium, high, max earners) or custom earnings profiles, with optional spousal
    benefits. Uses data from the Social Security Trustees Report.
